T1  - POSITIVELY RESPONSIVE COLLECTIVE CHOICE RULES AND MAJORITY RULE: A GENERALIZATION OF MAY'S THEOREM TO MANY ALTERNATIVES
AU  - Horan, Sean
AU  - Osborne, Martin J.
AU  - Sanver, M. Remzi
Y1  - 2019/11/01
PY  - 2019
DA  - 2019/11/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12394
