T1  - FERTILITY SHOCKS AND EQUILIBRIUM MARRIAGE-RATE DYNAMICS
AU  - Knowles, John
AU  - Vandenbroucke, Guillaume
Y1  - 2019/11/01
PY  - 2019
DA  - 2019/11/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12395
T2  - International Economic Review
