T1  - APPARENT BIAS: WHAT DOES ATTITUDE POLARIZATION SHOW?
AU  - Benoît, Jean-Pierre
AU  - Dubra, Juan
Y1  - 2019/11/01
PY  - 2019
DA  - 2019/11/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12400
