T1  - DIMENSIONALITY AND DISAGREEMENT: ASYMPTOTIC BELIEF DIVERGENCE IN RESPONSE TO COMMON INFORMATION
AU  - Loh, Isaac
AU  - Phelan, Gregory
Y1  - 2019/11/01
PY  - 2019
DA  - 2019/11/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12406
